= Enemies =

This page documents all regular enemies and mini-bosses in Kirby's Adventure for the NES.

== Enemy Data Structure ==

Each enemy entry uses 16 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Enemy ID
|-
| $01 || 1 || HP
|-
| $02 || 1 || Damage
|-
| $03 || 1 || Movement Type
|-
| $04 || 1 || Copy Ability Given
|-
| $05 || 1 || AI Pattern
|-
| $06 || 2 || Sprite Pointer
|-
| $08-$0F || 8 || Animation/Behavior Data
|}

