|-
| Grand Wheelie || 10 || Wheel || Rolls, jumps || ICI, OO
|-
| Meta Knight || 8 || Sword* || Sword combos || BB, GG, OO
|-
| Mr. Frosty || 10 || Freeze || Throws ice blocks || ICI, BB, RR
|-
| Paint Roller || 8 || (Various) || Paints enemies that attack || Various
